<plot>Based on an operetta by Kálmán, Emmerich (qv) "Das Veilchen vom Montmartre" which in turn was inspired by Puccini's "La bohème". This is a story of three struggling artists: a painter, a poet, and a composer, living in a bohemian Montmartre district of Paris. They help a poor flower girl, Violette, to find shelter, when she is thrown out by her landlord.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?436729</url></doc>
